social_posts.post_text: 🔥HTV HOT EVENT ALERT: This Wednesday, 10.18 starting at 6PM, join HTV Host @michellesoudry, Hadas Levy, Bri Teresi, former IDF Special Forces Officers and South Floridians coming together to raise funds to directly equip the more than 300,00 IDF Troops called to front line duty in dire need of lifesaving gear and immediate aid to fight the war against terrorism. Israel Strong Foundation is a non-profit organization founded by former IDF Special Forces Officers, with a mission of assisting the IDF. Limited tickets available $100 PP, with 100% proceeds directly benefitting the cause. Follow @houseofgabtv for more special event coverage and to be in-the-know on Who & What’s Trending, HOT & NOT in South Florida. #military #aid #southflorida

It’s been 12 days since the horrific Terror attack on my beloved homeland of Israel. 12 days of crying, 12 days of praying heavily that the hostages will be returned home, 12 days of worrying about my family and all of Israel, 12 days of worrying about the future threats here in America, 12 days of praying that our IDF can destroy the terrorist organizations that threaten not only Israel but the whole world. The only thing that has been a light in the last 12 days is seeing the unity and support from so many. I wanted to thank everyone who has donated and supported to the @israelstrongusa foundation who has been helping aid the IDF with the life saving equipment they need to fight the war against terror. We will see you all tonight at Save A Soldier Gala presented by Israel Strong Foundation  at Founders Shooting club and thank you so much to everyone who has donated to make this happen. 100 % of tonight’s proceeds go directly to the IDF. #amisraelchai #godblessisrael #godblesstheidf #godblessamerica #thankyou #saveasoldiergala @ssctactical1 @foundersshootingclub @hulbertwaldroup @photobykate1 @peterizzo_ @briteresi @sarabnewton @thetechconsultant1 @drawarms @thehouseofgab @djshaqfx @stevenavielgato @aaronsmith_realtor @kavitachanne
Mayor of Aventura Fla & Mayor of Hollywood Fla - save a soldier gala ✡️

Israel Strong Foundation presents Save A Soldier Gala was tremendously successful in raising close to $200,000 to help aid the IDF with the life saving supplies they need. As many of you know, the war in Israel is not anticipated to end soon. Many of the reserve soldiers who have been drafted are in need of equipment and Israel Strong Foundation’s mission is to help as many soldiers possible, get the equipment they need. That is why they are donating 100% of the proceeds to the IDF. I want to thank everyone who attended and everyone who donated. A huge thank you to everyone who donated their time and supplies to volunteer! Thank you to Mayor of Aventura Howard Weinberg and Mayor of Hollywood Josh Levy for your moving speeches, As well as all our other speakers. #shabbatshalom #saveasoldiergala #amisraelchai #godblesstheidf #godblessisrael #godblessamerica #southflorida #foundersshootingclub thank you @photobykate1 for the amazing pictures!! 🙏🙏🙏
